premise_source_doc_sentence: La Vérendrye wildlife reserve is one of the largest reserves in the province of Quebec , Canada , covering 12,589 square kilometres of contiguous land and lake area  (  Assinica wildlife reserve is the largest in the province , but its territory is broken up in four non-contiguous parts  )  .
Pauatahanui Wildlife Reserve is a wetland reserve located in Pauatahanui and on the eastern edge of the Pauatahanui Inlet of the Porirua Harbour in Porirua , New Zealand .

Two First Nation communities are found within the boundaries of the wildlife reserve : Kitcisakik on Great Victoria Lake and Lac-Rapide on Cabonga Reservoir .
